aspguidp.service.output

Class Time_informationTime_unit2ValueDataServicePool

  • java.lang.Object
    • aspguidp.service.data.DataServicePool
      • aspguidp.service.output.Time_informationTime_unit2ValueDataServicePool

  • public class Time_informationTime_unit2ValueDataServicePool
extends DataServicePool
    Singleton data service pool of a specific entity/value.

    This class is generated for each input entity, output entity, input value and output value of the application by the aspguid compiler. It provides methods to access data related services, managers and other data related information for the entity/value.

      • getEntityDataManager

        public EntityDataManager getEntityDataManager()
        Method to access the entity data manager instance for the entity/value of the service pool instance. If the entity data manager is not initialized yet, it is initialized before it is returned.

        If the entity/value of the service pool is an input entity/value, the entity data manager is registered to the input atom hub as atom consumer and atom supplier. If the entity/value of the service pool is an output entity/value, the entity data manager is registered to the output atom hub as atom consumer.
